FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend Senate Bill No. 1611 as follows:
1. On Page 2, Line 21, by deleting after the word “company”, the word “or” and inserting
the word “producing”;
2. On Page 3, Lines 15 through 20, by deleting after the word “means” on Line 15 and
before the semi-colon on Line 20, all language, and inserting the words “the People’s
Republic of China, the Russian Federation, the Islamic Republic of Iran, the Democratic
People’s Republic of Korea, the Republic of Cuba, the Venezuelan regime of Nicolás
Maduro, or the Syrian Arab Republic”; and
3. On Page 5, Line 9, by inserting before the word “submitted”, the word “knowingly”.
